sequenceDiagram
    participant User as Data Scientist
    participant DSPA as DSPA<br/>KFP Runtime
    participant Init as Init Container<br/>(pipelines-components)
    participant KFP as KFP API Server
    participant TaskPod as KFP Task Pod
    participant PVC as Shared PVC<br/>(50Gi nfs-csi RWX)
    participant S3 as S3 Storage<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant HF as Hugging Face Hub<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant LlamaStack as Llama Stack API<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant ModelReg as Model Registry<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant K8sAPI as Kubernetes API<br/>6443/TCP HTTPS

    rect rgb(230, 240, 255)
        Note over Init,KFP: Flow 4: Init Container Startup
        Init->>Init: Read /app/managed-pipelines.json
        Init->>KFP: Copy compiled YAMLs to<br/>/config/managed-pipelines/<br/>(shared volume, filesystem)
        KFP->>KFP: Discover & register<br/>managed pipelines
    end

    rect rgb(255, 245, 230)
        Note over User,S3: Flow 1: AutoML Tabular Training Pipeline
        User->>DSPA: Submit AutoML Tabular Pipeline
        DSPA->>TaskPod: Schedule data loader pod
        TaskPod->>S3: Download dataset<br/>HTTPS/443, TLS 1.2+<br/>Auth: AWS IAM credentials
        S3-->>TaskPod: Dataset CSV/Parquet
        TaskPod->>PVC: Write dataset to shared workspace
        DSPA->>TaskPod: Schedule AutoGluon training pod<br/>(odh-automl image)
        TaskPod->>PVC: Read dataset, write models
        TaskPod->>TaskPod: AutoGluon model training<br/>& selection
        DSPA->>TaskPod: Schedule leaderboard pod
        TaskPod->>PVC: Read model artifacts
        TaskPod->>KFP: Upload leaderboard artifact<br/>HTTPS/443, SA Token
    end

    rect rgb(230, 255, 230)
        Note over User,ModelReg: Flow 2: Fine-Tuning Pipeline (LoRA/SFT/OSFT)
        User->>DSPA: Submit fine-tuning pipeline
        DSPA->>TaskPod: Schedule dataset download pod
        TaskPod->>HF: Download model & dataset<br/>HTTPS/443, TLS 1.2+<br/>Auth: Bearer Token (HF_TOKEN)
        HF-->>TaskPod: Model weights & dataset
        TaskPod->>PVC: Write to shared PVC<br/>(50Gi, nfs-csi, RWX)
        DSPA->>TaskPod: Schedule training pod (GPU)
        TaskPod->>PVC: Read data, train model
        TaskPod->>TaskPod: Training via<br/>unsloth/mini-trainer/instructlab
        TaskPod->>PVC: Write fine-tuned model
        DSPA->>TaskPod: Schedule lm-eval pod
        TaskPod->>PVC: Read model artifacts
        TaskPod->>TaskPod: Evaluate with lm-eval harness
        DSPA->>TaskPod: Schedule model registration pod
        TaskPod->>ModelReg: Register model with provenance<br/>HTTPS/443, TLS 1.2+<br/>Auth: Bearer Token (K8s SA)
    end

    rect rgb(255, 230, 245)
        Note over User,LlamaStack: Flow 3: AutoRAG Document Optimization Pipeline
        User->>DSPA: Submit AutoRAG pipeline
        DSPA->>TaskPod: Schedule test data loader pod
        TaskPod->>S3: Download test data<br/>HTTPS/443, AWS IAM
        DSPA->>TaskPod: Schedule documents discovery pod
        TaskPod->>S3: Discover documents<br/>HTTPS/443, AWS IAM
        DSPA->>TaskPod: Schedule text extraction pod<br/>(odh-autorag image)
        TaskPod->>TaskPod: Docling extracts text<br/>(PDF, DOCX, PPTX, HTML)
        DSPA->>TaskPod: Schedule RAG optimization pod<br/>(odh-autorag image)
        TaskPod->>LlamaStack: Generate embeddings<br/>HTTPS/443, TLS 1.2+<br/>Auth: API Key
        LlamaStack-->>TaskPod: Embedding vectors
        TaskPod->>TaskPod: ChromaDB indexing<br/>(in-process)
        TaskPod->>TaskPod: ai4rag template optimization
        DSPA->>TaskPod: Schedule leaderboard pod
        TaskPod->>KFP: Upload evaluation artifact<br/>HTTPS/443, SA Token
    end
